        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"11月27日，宏福苑居民楼仍在冒烟\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r8W33JodimUlNnROYo.bew--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cfdd2feabff323571aa240aaa6a48d6d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">11月27日，宏福苑居民楼仍在冒烟</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">致命大火</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">共有八棟高樓的香港大埔宏福苑發生重大火災，目前已有數十人死亡、數百人失聯。這個屋苑近期正在進行強制性檢修，據當地官員稱，工程所用的竹制腳手架是起火點。作為該工程的承保方，中國太平股價下跌，不過香港專業保險經紀協會主席稱，財產全險和特定工程險都「嚴重投保不足」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"11月27日，宏福苑居民樓仍在冒煙Photographer: Lam Yik/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/osGwQfXho8MacPGIH1U0TQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/24b9dc4fca79d261245cb7b76c76f9b0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">11月27日，宏福苑居民樓仍在冒煙Photographer: Lam Yik/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">提振消費</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在經濟依然承壓之際，中國多部門印發了《關於增強消費品供需適配性進一步促進消費的實施方案》的通知，提及拓展多元興趣消費供給，積極發展寵物周邊、動漫、潮服潮玩等興趣消費產品等內容，泡泡瑪特等潮玩概念股應聲大漲。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-205a0ce5-7002-391d-be65-58abff1e5d27-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">尋求展期</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">萬科隔夜宣布尋求12月15日到期的20億元人民幣債券展期，引發美元債創新低，境內債再度大跌停牌，A股和H股雙雙下挫。不過該公司多只境內債在場外協商交易中成交價隨後大幅反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">裁員繼續</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">從蘋果公司、荷蘭銀行，到惠普、麥肯錫再到太古，多家公司本周傳出裁員新消息。原因各種各樣，有的是因為業務調整，有的是因為業績不佳，但是AI替代仍然是個大主題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「不要挑釁」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據媒體引述知情人士報導，習近平在本周與川普長達一小時的電話中，用了近半時間強調中國對台灣的主權，以及中美共同維護世界秩序的責任；隨後，川普與日本首相通話，告知高市早苗不要在台灣主權問題上挑釁中國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-054138593.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 14:35:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日本沒有直接評論川普是否要求不要在台灣問題上挑釁中國的提問",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 對於有關美國總統唐納德·川普是否建議日本首相高市早苗避免在台灣問題上激怒中國的提問，日本政府首席發言人沒有直接回答。此前有報導稱雙方曾進行過此類交流。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我無法就外交政策相關的交流作進一步評論。」日本內閣官房長官木原稔周四在例行記者會上被問及該報導是否屬實，他表示，在本周川普與高市的通話中，「兩位領導人確認了美日之間的密切合作」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《華爾街日報》此前報導稱，川普在通話中建議高市不要在台灣主權問題上挑釁北京。報導引述了未具名日本官員和一位了解通話情況的美國人。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-61e29c92-a3fe-3065-be54-3dd94bef8723-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：日本首相高市早苗稱之前談及台灣問題時並未打算提及任何細節</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan Avoids Comment on Whether Trump Asked Not to Provoke China</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%8C%91%E9%87%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F-030309022.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 11:50:58",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國太平股價下跌 因其承保了發生重大火災的香港宏福苑檢修工程",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國太平股價周四下跌，因為香港大埔宏福苑發生的致命大火給該保險公司帶來賠付問題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司股價早盤一度下跌8.1%，截至香港時間上午11:58，跌幅收窄至不到2%。中國太平是宏福苑強制性樓宇及窗戶檢查工程的第三者責任和員工賠償承保方。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項3.16億港元（4100萬美元）的建築工程使用了竹制腳手架和大量防護網，目前政府正在開展調查，以確定其與這場18個小時仍未撲滅的火災之間的關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：香港發生60多年來最嚴重住宅火災 造成至少44人死亡、數百人失蹤</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c3ff0663-9366-375d-a988-811af3615923-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國太平的保單覆蓋了全部合同金額，外加5,000萬港元（640萬美元）事故保障。該保險公司還為該工程提供2億港元的員工賠償保障。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外，中國太平還有一份20億港元財產全險保單。該公司的代表拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港專業保險經紀協會麥順邦接受電話採訪稱，鑒於這個擁有約2000套住宅的屋苑檢修工程巨大，財產全險和特定工程險都「嚴重投保不足」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">麥順邦表示，公共區域和電梯鋼纜的重建費用幾乎肯定會超過保額。他補充說，業主可以就保單中5000萬港元的意外險部分申請身故和傷害賠償，但考慮到目前的死亡人數且仍有數百人下落不明，這一金額「遠遠不夠」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Taiping Insurance Falls on Deadly Hong Kong Fire Liability</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Kelly Li、Felix Tam、Jiyeun Lee、Dingmin Zhang.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E5%9B%A0%E5%85%B6%E6%89%BF%E4%BF%9D%E4%BA%86%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E7%81%BD%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%AE%8F%E7%A6%8F%E8%8B%91%E6%AA%A2%E4%BF%AE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B-042915910.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 14:15:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "安踏據悉考慮對彪馬的潛在競購",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士稱，中國運動服裝公司安踏體育是考慮潛在競購彪馬的公司之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，安踏在與顧問合作，評估對彪馬的競購方案。由於信息未公開，知情人士要求匿名。部分知情人士表示，如果安踏決定推進競購，可能會與一家私募股權公司合作。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，其他潛在競購者可能包括安踏的競爭對手李寧，李寧已在與銀行商討融資方案，對彪馬進行了初步評估。知情人士還表示，彪馬也可能吸引日本亞瑟士等運動服裝公司的興趣。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9e20853a-5122-3a31-b6b7-5e3d76edf587-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，目前討論尚處於初步階段，不清楚哪些競購者會繼續推進。他們還表示，彪馬最大股東——法國億萬富豪Pinault家族的估值預期，可能會成為任何交易的重大障礙。今年以來，彪馬在法蘭克福的股價已下跌62%，公司市值目前為25億歐元（約合29億美元）。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據公司年報顯示，截至去年底，Pinault家族的Artémis控股公司持有彪馬29%的股權。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">安踏的代表沒有回應置評請求，Artémis、亞瑟士和彪馬的代表未置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">李寧在回應彭博新聞社的詢問時表示，公司仍專注於自身品牌的發展，並未就有關彪馬進行任何實質性談判或評估。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Anta Sports Is Said to Explore Potential Bid for Puma</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Will Davies、Manuel Baigorri、Kanoko Matsuyama、Tim Loh、Angelina Rascouet、Daniela Wei.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%89%E8%B8%8F%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%B0%8D%E5%BD%AA%E9%A6%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%BD%9B%E5%9C%A8%E7%AB%B6%E8%B3%BC-031654599.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 12:10:48",
