            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "摩通私人銀行料標普500指數到明年底有望上漲20%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 美國股市過去四天4%的漲幅，讓那些警告全面回調即將到來的空頭們暫時消聲，如今股市多頭又開始趾高氣昂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通私人銀行表示，標普500指數有望在2026年延續其多年來的強勁上漲勢頭。該指數今年迄今已上漲16%，而前兩年的漲幅均至少達到23%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司的基線預測是，經濟成長再次加速、企業盈利強勁、人工智能技術穩步發展將推動該指數明年升至7,400點，較當前水平有約9%的上行空間。若這些利好因素足夠強勁，該指數甚至有望飆升至8,200點，意味著從現在到明年底將有20%的漲幅。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-30ed41f2-24ad-34aa-8b09-3fa7b24f5ddf-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/q191FeM3cKXegiFaKNFppg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e5406696d9ed892580a8dadb8b9b83a2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番樂觀預測出爐之際，華爾街正因人工智能發展前景和經濟疲軟跡象而神經緊繃。該公司美國投資策略主管Jacob Manoukian和全球投資策略聯席主管Stephen Parker認為，近期市場動盪導致標普500指數較10月觸及的紀錄高點下跌5%，這證實市場並沒有陷入泡沫通常伴隨的狂熱狀態。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們很多客戶目前都手握大量現金，對於這些客戶，我們著眼未來12至18個月：這正是投資良機，」 Parker周二接受採訪時表示。「我們認為這是一個買入機會，但也認可這未必是市場底部。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家私人銀行的樂觀預期與其投銀股票研究團隊的觀點一致。摩根大通策略師Dubravko Lakos-Bujas預計，在強勁盈利成長和聯儲會降息推動下，標普500指數到2026年底將從當前水平上漲約10%至7,500點——若通膨降溫使官員們能夠實施超過兩次降息，該指數甚至可能上衝至8,000點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金融機構的早期預測顯示，它們對2026年前景普遍樂觀。德意志銀行的Binky Chadha預計標普500指數到2026年底將上漲約18%至8,000點。Michael Wilson帶領的摩根士丹利策略師團隊預計該指數一年後將升至7,800點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管摩根大通私人銀行對明年前景展現出強烈樂觀的看法，但策略師們也考慮到了一種悲觀情景：如果人工智能主題和經濟出現疲軟，標普500指數可能會最低跌至4,600點，跌幅約32%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題JPMorgan Private Bank’s Bull Case Has S&amp;P 500 Up 20% by 2027 (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A4%A7%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%94%B1%E5%A4%9A%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1-%E6%96%99%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE500%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%88%B0%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B220-005122309.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-27 10:30:52",
