        {
            "title": "中國更多地方給學生放假 以期帶動家長增加支出",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"中國更多地方給學生放假 以期帶動家長增加支出\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XaIE3DRNV9ElX7OZTdiZaA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/46efafa0-cb2f-11f0-bfea-bd38aad1bbd5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">中國更多地方給學生放假 以期帶動家長增加支出</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E7%B5%A6%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%94%BE%E5%81%87-%E4%BB%A5%E6%9C%9F%E5%B8%B6%E5%8B%95%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA-233809159.html",
